condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Cooperation Agreement | Description :The Government will execute a cooperation agreement with SPN (once created)under grant terms and conditions approved by the Association. | Due Date :15-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :Establishment of the SPN Fiduciary Unit | Description :The Government will create the Project Fiduciary Unit,established within SPN to run the day-to-day fiduciary management and planning of the Project, with staffing, terms of reference,composition and powers as further described in the Project Implementation. | Due Date :15-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :Establishment of the SPN | Description :The Government will establish the board of the SPN, which will play therole of Steering Committee to provide overall coordination and supervision for the Project, fiduciary and governance oversight andapproval of the Annual Work Programs, with terms of reference, composition and powers as further described in the ProjectImplementation Manual. | Due Date :15-Mar-2015
Finance Agreement :External Audit | Description :The Government will recruit independent auditors to carry out the audit on thefinancial statements related to the project. | Due Date :15-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :Recruitment of three Project Focal Points | Description :The Government will recruit three Project Focal Points(MINPTNTIC, MINPORTFOLIO and ARPTC), to provide oversight of all technical, social, and environmental matters relating to Projectimplementation; planning of Project activities and preparation of Annual Work Programs; monitoring and evaluation of Projectactivities including quality assurance. | Due Date :24-Jan-2015
